      <scopecontent id="aspace_517c18749393d667585afd47c07cb9ac">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The material consists of mounted photographs of Frank Moore (Yale 1868) of members of the Class of 1868, some of whom are identified, and scenes of buildings and grounds at Yale and in New Haven. Included are scenes of Temple and Chapel Streets, the Old Campus, and the cave of the three judges on West Rock.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
